    A GroupedDataset of UKBenchListDatasets instances each of an item in the UKBench experiment. UKBench can be provided in any form supported by VFS The UKBench files must be in one flat directory and named "ukbenchXXXXX.jpg"
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
